The first things that came to mid seeing this problem was a recursive approach
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
just go to every possible candiates check its credibility and check again from the next candiate by deleting the duplicate elemnts after a same element has been visited.
# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n^2)
