Part 1 | Part 2
.........O..........
Part 3 | Part4

O - is the middle element.

If target is more than O - then we ignore Part1 otherwise we ignore Part 3 - and continue recursively to search in parts, to simplify code and speed up execution time - I merge neighbor parts.

