***Intuition*** :
It is given that all rows and columns are sorted i.e.
1. Along any row if we move right we'll get bigger numbers and if we move left we'll get smaller numbers.
2. Along any column if we move down we'll get bigger numbers and if we move up we'll get smaller numbers.

So we'll start from TOP-RIGHT corner and cancel out a row or a column each time.

***Example***
